title: [Empath Guild]
description: Sheer curtains billow to life from the occasional night breeze, glimmering in the dim torchlight.  Silk banners line the ivory walls, prominently displaying the names of past Guildmasters of the guild in flowery script.

Just beyond an open window, a pair of small grey doves tends to their nest, cooing quietly.  Silk banners line the ivory walls, prominently displaying the names of past Guildmasters of the guild in flowery script.
